# ── Claude Code shared configuration ──────────────────────────────────
# Shared content is committed to git (available to all teams).
# Porting-specific items are symlinked from ai-prompts and auto-ignored.
#
# HOW TO ADD A NEW SHARED FILE:
#   1. Add a !whitelist entry below for the file/directory
#   2. Run: git add -f .claude/path/to/file
#   3. Commit normally
#
# HOW TO ADD A NEW PORTING FILE:
#   Just add it to ai-prompts — it's auto-ignored here. No changes needed.

# .claude/ — ignore all, then whitelist shared items
.claude/*
!.claude/settings.json
!.claude/rules/
.claude/rules/*
!.claude/rules/architecture/
!.claude/skills/
.claude/skills/*
!.claude/skills/test-runner/
!.claude/skills/visual-verification/
!.claude/skills/app-runner/
!.claude/skills/log-inspector/
!.claude/skills/papi-client/
!.claude/scripts/
.claude/scripts/*
!.claude/scripts/statusline.sh
!.claude/README.md

# .context/ — ignore all, then whitelist shared items
.context/*
!.context/architecture/
!.context/Paratext10-Overview.md
!.context/README.md
!.context/standards/
.context/standards/*
!.context/standards/Architecture.md
!.context/standards/Code-Review-Guide.md
!.context/standards/Code-Style-Guide.md
!.context/standards/Component-Builder-Patterns.md
!.context/standards/Component-Selection-Quick-Reference.md
!.context/standards/Entry-Point-Guide.md
!.context/standards/Extension-Development-Guide.md
!.context/standards/Git-Guide.md
!.context/standards/Localization-Guide.md
!.context/standards/Paranext-Core-Patterns.md
!.context/standards/Security-Guide.md
!.context/standards/Testing-Guide.md

